Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.03,Curerpp_ML,,0,0,0,,Full Full Full Full Linkru !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:31.03,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}心有灵犀 指引我们 紧密相连！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.63,Magical_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}プリキュア エクストリーム レインボー！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.63,Curerpp_ML,,0,0,0,,Precure Extreme Rainbow !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:35.63,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\b1}光美·绚烂彩虹！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.91,DarkMHS_JP,,0,0,0,,力が戻ったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.91,DarkMHS_CN,,0,0,0,,找回力量了吗？
