Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.93,Ha_Chan_JP,,0,0,0,,時の停止が始まってる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.93,Ha_Chan_CN,,0,0,0,,时间的停滞 开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.17,Miracle_JP,,0,0,0,,そんな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.17,Miracle_CN,,0,0,0,,怎么会
